-Endless new resolutions and devices are difficult to support separately for a web developer 
-Responsive design is a way for a web developer to make his website adapt to all devices and resolutions
-Responsive design is a necessity and not a luxury anymore!

Various ways to achieve responsive designs
-Setting up the viewport
-Use max-width/max-height
-Using CSS Media Queries(When screen gets re-sized, you can inject different CSS  properties)
-Using rem/vh/vw units over pixels